data.name: AS_3TECN113_GC
data.queryText:
SELECT TOP 10 PERCENT 
       tmp.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC AS 'ContactKey',
       'AS_3TECN113_Email_Tecnoprecios_Persona_20231113' AS 'JourneyId',
       'AS_3TECN113_Email_Tecnoprecios_Persona_20231113' AS 'JourneyVersionId',
       'AS_3TECN113_Email_Tecnoprecios_Persona_20231113' AS 'JourneyName',
       ' {{mcpm:CODIGO_OBJETIVO}}' AS 'CodObjetivo',
       GetDate() AS 'Timestamp'
FROM (
    SELECT t1.*
    FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b62ddd4-0e82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b62ddd4-0e82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t1
    LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/2c0d03ab-9a7e-e811-a2c7-1402ec9607c0/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/2c0d03ab-9a7e-e811-a2c7-1402ec9607c0/data/name}}] t2 ON t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC = t2.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC
    WHERE t2.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC IS NULL
    /*AND t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC IN ('000000017012761700', '000000005627038200', '000000006763329700', '000000006723518400')*/
) tmp
ORDER BY NEWID()

data.name: AS_3TECN113_AUD
data.queryText:
SELECT t1.*
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b62ddd4-0e82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b62ddd4-0e82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t1
LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b456ce13-4c82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b456ce13-4c82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t2 ON t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC = T2.ContactKey
LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b656ce13-4c82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/b656ce13-4c82-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t3 ON t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC = t3.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC
WHERE t2.ContactKey IS NULL
AND t3.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC IS NULL
